                <h2>Introduction</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>"In the fiercely competitive landscape of global marketing, the stability of your Google Ads account directly determines the continuity of your advertising campaigns and return on investment. Once an account is suspended, advertisers not only face traffic interruption but may also miss critical business windows."</p>
