<li>Collect competitors' violation evidence</li>
<li>Submit complaints through Google's brand protection channel</li>
<li>Clearly explain the situation in appeals</li>
</ol>
<h3>4.2 Sensitive Industry Compliance Strategy</h3>
<p>For <strong>financial, medical, health, alcohol, gambling</strong>, and other sensitive industries, Google has stricter review standards:</p>
<ul>
<li>Must clearly display qualification certificates on landing pages</li>
<li>Ad copy must include risk warnings</li>
<li>Target audience must have age restrictions</li>
<li>Some regions prohibit advertising, requiring precise geographic targeting</li>
</ul>
<h3>4.3 Quick Recovery from Mistaken Suspensions</h3>
<p>If suspension is due to system misjudgment (such as malicious reports from competitors):</p>
<ol>
