<li>Policy update notification emails</li>
<li>Google Ads Partner Community</li>
</ul>
<h3>5.2 Technical Protection Measures</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>IP distribution management</strong>: Team members using fixed IPs operate main accounts, other testing uses independent IPs</li>
<li><strong>Browser fingerprint isolation</strong>: Use professional tools to isolate different account operating environments</li>
<li><strong>Operation log auditing</strong>: Record all account operations for problem tracing</li>
</ul>
